{"tid":737550,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4]FIFA18 pro club開新隊 誠徵一班隊友重新上路","createTime":"2018-07-11T02:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T10:20:09.000Z","uid":193445,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"8340b86e75445dbbc40e907aeb8f5e6900a880cc","tid":737550,"uid":193445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T02:30:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">希望可以收一班有心既full time隊友長玩長夾由零開始重新上路  <br />\n<br />\n大家可以一齊開mic吹下水 溝通下<br />\n 隊友玩得唔好可以提醒下一齊討論<br />\n<br />\n時間: 只要夠4人日日都可以開波 <br />\n<br />\n球隊風格:主要打返控球短傳  到時可以再夾<br />\n<br />\n位置:新隊除左st咩位都招 希望大家可以打反最擅長既位<br />\n (因為小弟係打st既)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入隊要求:最好有pro club經驗 有teamwork  唔會1個扭11個 唔會過份獨食  不過份個人主義 唔需要球王/教練  新手都可以入只要想進步肯學肯聽意見<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既就快d留低tg啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"c406bfb3d6ef1edbbd970e7fb439ac5d29cf5feb","tid":737550,"uid":193445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df0f5e1a893c353fe08d0bff3a2ce0a9124cc24","tid":737550,"uid":193445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:55:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281232f40dee0e7e7b6b86b08c964a001c46b81f","tid":737550,"uid":193445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:21:05.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3e1679bf50abdb4527b15581a0f7372c2d989b","tid":737550,"uid":1035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:36:24.000Z","msg":"想同唔同人夾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/fac